            "description": "Monitor threads. \n- Busy: Threads actively processing a request.\n- Current: Total threads allocated by Tomcat (grows up to Max).\n- Config Max: The ceiling (200).\nIf 'Busy' hits 'Config Max', new requests will queue up.",
